[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    518[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Synthetic Consumption Data
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    519[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    520[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Real consumption history comes out of the materials-management ledger, the OR case-cart system, and the inpatient pharmacy. None of that data should be checked into a code repo. For the demo we generate synthetic SKU consumption with the same demand patterns the real data has: smooth high-volume gloves, intermittent specialty kits, procedure-driven implants, and a couple of misbehaving outliers. The synthetic generator below is deterministic given the seed so the demo's segmentation and forecast outputs are reproducible.
