[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    527[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                                      seed=20260415) -> dict:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    528[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """Generate ~2 years of synthetic per-SKU daily
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    529[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     consumption plus a small SKU master, a calendar of
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    530[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     holidays, and a forecasted-cases timeseries for the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    531[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     procedure-driven SKU. Returns a dict the rest of the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    532[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     pipeline consumes."""
