[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     896[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     897[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Each segment routes to a model family appropriate for its demand pattern. The demo uses hand-rolled implementations of Holt-Winters exponential smoothing, Croston's method, and the Syntetos-Boylan approximation so the example runs without Prophet, statsmodels, or SageMaker. Production replaces each branch with the real fit:
