[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     902[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Procedure-driven**: A two-stage model that consumes the case-volume forecast from Recipe 12.5 (or wherever case forecasts live) and applies a per-case usage rate.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     903[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Pooled multi-SKU**: SageMaker's built-in DeepAR algorithm trained on the smooth-segment SKUs as a single related-series model.
